# Handoff — Pack #5 (Knowledge Engine) Phase 4 complete

## What was done

**Phase 4 (Integration + docs) of Pack #5
(`knowledge-engine-json-store`) is
code-complete.** A real `Kernel` now boots
with a real `JsonKnowledgeAdapter` against a
`tempfile::TempDir`, runs end-to-end
`find_information` + `store_information` +
`list_topics` calls, and the `EventBus`
publishes the 3 audit events with matching
`correlation_id`. The conformance suite in
`afa-knowledge` runs against both the
in-crate `MockAdapter` AND the real
`JsonKnowledgeAdapter`. The
`docs/engines/Knowledge.md` and
`docs/CONTEXT.md` are re-aligned with the
on-disk reality (per-record `.md` files in
per-topic folders + a single
`<root>/.index.json`). A new
`docs/plugins/KnowledgeJson.md` mirrors
`docs/plugins/LlmHttp.md`.

## Where the work landed

**New files:**

- `crates/afa-kernel/tests/knowledge_integration.rs` —
  5 end-to-end tests that wire a real
  `Kernel` + real `CapabilityRegistry` +
  real `JsonKnowledgeAdapter` over a real
  `EventBus`:
  (1) `store_then_find_round_trip` —
  `store_information` then
  `find_information` returns the new
  record with the expected shape.
  (2) `list_topics_empty_then_after_store` —
  empty list before any store, then one
  topic after one store.
  (3) `store_find_list_round_trip` — the
  full FLOW doc sequence; verifies the 3
  events are published with matching
  `correlation_id`.
  (4) `describe_capabilities_is_static` —
  the JSON adapter's reported capabilities
  are stable + match the locked
  `KnowledgeCapabilities` shape.
  (5) `kernel_without_knowledge_returns_error` —
  `Kernel::knowledge("default")` returns
  `Err(KernelError::NoKnowledgeAdapter)`
  if `register_knowledge()` was never
  called.
- `docs/plugins/KnowledgeJson.md` —
  mirrors `docs/plugins/LlmHttp.md`
  (Purpose / Responsibilities /
  Capability Reporting / What Changes
  Here vs. Elsewhere / Configuration /
  Boot Resilience).

**Modified files:**

- `crates/afa-kernel/src/kernel.rs` —
  `Kernel` gained `register_knowledge()`
  + `knowledge()` accessors. The
  `Kernel::knowledge(key)` method is
  symmetric to `Kernel::llm(key)`: returns
  `Arc<dyn KnowledgeV1>` and propagates
  the underlying `CapabilityRegistry`
  error (`KernelError::NoKnowledgeAdapter`
  if the capability was never registered,
  `KernelError::UnknownKnowledgeKey { key }`
  if the key is unknown).
- `crates/afa-kernel/src/lib.rs` —
  re-exports `KnowledgeV1` (mirroring the
  `LlmV1` re-export pattern, so
  downstream code can `use afa_kernel::
  {Kernel, KnowledgeV1}` without
  touching `afa-contracts`).
- `crates/afa-kernel/Cargo.toml` —
  added `afa-plugin-knowledge-json` as
  a `dev-dependency` (the real adapter
  is needed for the integration test;
  a test-only `MockAdapter` is not
  enough — see `PHILOSOPHY.md` "Test
  the engine, not the harness").
- `crates/afa-knowledge/Cargo.toml` —
  added `afa-plugin-knowledge-json` as
  a `dev-dependency`, plus `afa-bus`
  (the real adapter needs a real
  `EventBus` to publish the audit
  events) and `uuid` (the real-impl
  conformance test parses the on-disk
  `<record_id>.md` filename to assert
  the on-disk side effect of the
  conformance suite's canned
  `store_information` call).
- `crates/afa-knowledge/tests/knowledge_v1.rs` —
  extended with 1 new test:
  `knowledge_v1_conformance_suite_against_json_adapter`
  — runs `run_conformance_suite` against
  the real `JsonKnowledgeAdapter` (not
  just the in-crate `MockAdapter`) and
  asserts the on-disk side effect
  (the `<record_id>.md` file is on disk
  after the canned `store_information`
  call, and `<storage_root>/.index.json`
  is parseable JSON with `schema_version:
  1`).
- `docs/engines/Knowledge.md` — re-aligned
  the on-disk layout section (per-record
  `.md` files in per-topic folders, not
  per-topic `.md` files), the
  `LoadOutcome` dispatch (Loaded /
  Missing / Corrupt + rebuild), the
  orphan-temp cleanup at boot, the
  `KnowledgeRecordInput` vs.
  `KnowledgeRecord` split (writer's
  view vs. reader's view, per TRD
  §2.2.2), and the
  `KnowledgeTopicsListed` event.
- `docs/CONTEXT.md` — added
  `KnowledgeRecordInput` (distinct
  from `KnowledgeRecord`), the
  `Knowledge Topics Listed Event`
  entry, and re-aligned the
  JSON/Markdown adapter's on-disk
  description.
- `docs/features/knowledge-engine-json-store/IMPL-knowledge-engine-json-store.md` —
  Phase 4 status flipped from
  `PENDING` to `DONE` with the full
  inventory in both the summary
  section (line ~265) and the
  detailed Phase 4 plan (line ~1510).
  Deferred items (the
  `search_throughput` benchmark and
  the `operator_backup.sh` shell
  script) are explicitly marked
  "Deferred to a future pack" with
  the rationale.

