## Work ethics followed

- Story-telling comments on every
  non-trivial function (the
  "plain English first" rule from
  [PHILOSOPHY.md](file:///home/spanexx/Shared/agents/PHILOSOPHY.md)).
- CID headers on every new type and
  function.
- No fake / tautological tests — every
  test asserts on observable behavior
  (file system state, on-disk `.md`
  files, on-disk `.index.json`, bus
  events, `KernelError` shapes).
- Validation gate is the single-command
  `make` entry point.
- v1 limitations documented inline
  (in the code, in the IMPL doc, in
  this handoff) so the next contributor
  doesn't have to re-derive them.

