  mirroring the LLM accessor pattern. New error variants: None —
  reuses KernelError::NoKnowledgeAdapter (unregistered) and
  UnknownKnowledgeKey (unknown key). Re-exports KnowledgeV1 from
  afa-contracts so downstream code can use afa_kernel::{Kernel,
  KnowledgeV1} without touching afa-contracts.

