  empty list, store → find → list w/ 3 events (KnowledgeQueried,
  KnowledgeRecordStored, KnowledgeTopicsListed), describe_capabilities,
  and the no-adapter-registered error path.

* afa-knowledge/tests/knowledge_v1.rs: extended with 1 real-impl
