* afa-kernel/Cargo.toml: afa-plugin-knowledge-json added as
  dev-dependency. afa-knowledge/Cargo.toml: afa-plugin-knowledge-json,
  afa-bus, uuid added as dev-dependencies.

* docs/engines/Knowledge.md: re-aligned the on-disk layout
  section (per-record .md files in per-topic folders, not
  per-topic .md files), the LoadOutcome dispatch, the orphan-temp
  cleanup at boot, the KnowledgeRecordInput vs. KnowledgeRecord
  split (writer's view vs. reader's view per TRD §2.2.2), and
  the KnowledgeTopicsListed event.

* docs/CONTEXT.md: added KnowledgeRecordInput, the Knowledge Topics
  Listed Event, and re-aligned the JSON/Markdown adapter's
  on-disk description.

* docs/plugins/KnowledgeJson.md (NEW): mirrors docs/plugins/LlmHttp.md
  (Purpose / Responsibilities / Capability Reporting / What Changes
  Here vs. Elsewhere / Configuration / Boot Resilience).

* IMPL: Phase 4 status PENDING -> DONE in both the summary section
  and the detailed Phase 4 plan. Deferred items (search_throughput
  benchmark + operator_backup.sh) explicitly marked with rationale.

* Validation: 348 tests, 0 failed (was 342, +6: 5 kernel
  integration + 1 real-impl conformance). All 4 gates green.
  make clean. cargo doc clean.
